; AudioSilo no longer requires a FontAwesome Pro token to build.
; Icons are vendored as plain SVG path data in src/components/ui/icon-data.ts and
; drawn with react-native-svg, so `npm install` here needs nothing private.
;
; FontAwesome Pro is now isolated to the optional icon generator, which has its own
; registry config: scripts/glyphs/.npmrc (see scripts/glyphs/README.md). You only
; need a token to add/regenerate an icon, not to build or run the app.
